# Cloudflare Pages cache rules (COMMENTS/cross-device freshness).
# HTML must always revalidate so every device — phone, tablet, laptop — pulls the
# newest page (and therefore the newest JS) on each load; no stale UI lingers.
# Content-hashed assets never change, so they cache forever for speed.

/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate

/_next/static/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/pagefind/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600

/brand/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400
